    <body style="background-color: white; padding: 10px;">
        <h1>Display a preview in a diagram view</h1>
        &lt;p&gt;As you are designing a view, you can already see a graphical representation of the view by switching to the &#39;Diagram&#39; tab.  &lt;br /&gt;On this tab, you can see diagram-level setting at the top: the default layout, whether edge labels will be shown or not, whether duplicates are allowed or not. &lt;br /&gt;You can also preview details of individual edges and nodes. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Follow these steps to display a preview of a node or edge while you are designing a view. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Open an asset page.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Traceability &amp;gt; Diagram&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;Wait until the diagram has rendered.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click &lt;img class=&quot;confluence-embedded-image&quot; src=&quot;/download/attachments/13177149/preview.png?version=1&amp;amp;modificationDate=1436456828588&amp;amp;api=v2&quot; data-image-src=&quot;/download/attachments/13177149/preview.png?version=1&amp;amp;modificationDate=1436456828588&amp;amp;api=v2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &amp;gt; Properties&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click the &lt;strong&gt;Diagram&lt;/strong&gt; tab.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click on a node or an edge.&lt;br /&gt;The preview of the selected object is displayed on the right.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;confluence-embedded-image&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; src=&quot;/download/attachments/13177153/diagram-view-preview-panel.png?version=1&amp;amp;modificationDate=1439411711820&amp;amp;api=v2&quot; data-image-src=&quot;/download/attachments/13177153/diagram-view-preview-panel.png?version=1&amp;amp;modificationDate=1439411711820&amp;amp;api=v2&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
    </body>
</html>